
# https://news.ycombinator.com/item?id=13397404
# Remove CSS
nmap s :emenu View.Page Style.No Style<CR>
# Restore CSS
nmap <S-s> :emenu View.Page Style.Basic Page Style<CR>


# https://www.howtogeek.com/268116/is-there-a-way-to-force-enable-reader-view-in-mozilla-firefox/
# Enable Reader mode
:command reader execute “open about:reader?url=” + content.location.href (And then you type :reader to get the Reader View)
:nmap :reader (A simple Ctrl+R and that is it)

